338
0:17:44.55,000 --> 0:17:46,000
con Yuval Harari,

339
0:17:46.871,000 --> 0:17:49,000
y hay ahí afuera una audiencia en Facebook Live.

340
0:17:50.279,000 --> 0:17:52,000
